{"id":"api/platform-server/PlatformConfig","title":"PlatformConfig","contents":"\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-server\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-server\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-server/PlatformConfig\", \"name\": \"PlatformConfig\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/platform-server\">@angular/platform-server</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/platform-server/src/tokens.ts?message=docs(platform-server)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L10-L59\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/platform-server/src/tokens.ts#L10-L59\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"platformconfig\">PlatformConfig<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#platformconfig\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">傳遞配置物件以初始化平台。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Config object passed to initialize the platform.</p>\n\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/platform-server/PlatformConfig\" class=\"code-anchor\">PlatformConfig</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#document\"><span class=\"member-name\">document</span>?: string</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#url\"><span class=\"member-name\">url</span>?: string</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#useAbsoluteUrl\"><span class=\"member-name\">useAbsoluteUrl</span>?: boolean</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#baseUrl\"><span class=\"member-name\">baseUrl</span>?: string</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a name=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>屬性</th>\n        <th>說明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"document\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">document</span>?: string</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">用於引導伺服器端應用程式的初始 DOM。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The initial DOM to use to bootstrap the server application.</p>\n\n</div>\n          \n          </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"url\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">url</span>?: string</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">當前應用程式狀態的 URL。這用於初始化平台的 location。如果設定了 <code>baseUrl</code>，則將覆蓋 <code>protocol</code>、<code>hostname</code>、<code>port</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The URL for the current application state. This is used for initializing\nthe platform's location. <code>protocol</code>, <code>hostname</code>, and <code>port</code> will be\noverridden if <code>baseUrl</code> is set.</p>\n\n</div>\n          \n          </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"useAbsoluteUrl\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">useAbsoluteUrl</span>?: boolean</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">是否在 HTTP 請求中將絕對 URL 附加到任何相對 URL 上。如果設定為 true，則此邏輯就會在稍後的請求中執行任何 HTTP 攔截器之前執行。如果啟用了此標誌，則必須提供 <code>baseUrl</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Whether to append the absolute URL to any relative HTTP requests. If set to\ntrue, this logic executes prior to any HTTP interceptors that may run later\non in the request. <code>baseUrl</code> must be supplied if this flag is enabled.</p>\n\n</div>\n          \n          </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"baseUrl\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">baseUrl</span>?: string</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">用於解析 HTTP 請求的絕對 URL 的基本 URL。如果 <code>useAbsoluteUrl</code> 為 true，則必須設定它，並且必須包含協議、主機名和可選埠。如果未啟用 <code>useAbsoluteUrl</code> 則此選項無效。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The base URL for resolving absolute URL for HTTP requests. It must be set\nif <code>useAbsoluteUrl</code> is true, and must consist of protocol, hostname,\nand optional port. This option has no effect if <code>useAbsoluteUrl</code> is not\nenabled.</p>\n\n</div>\n          \n          </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/platform-server\n - api/platform-server/INITIAL_CONFIG\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/platform-server\n - api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#baseUrl\n - api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#document\n - api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#instance-properties\n - api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#platformconfig\n - api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#url\n - api/platform-server/PlatformConfig#useAbsoluteUrl\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/platform-server/src/tokens.ts?message=docs(platform-server)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L10-L59\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/platform-server/src/tokens.ts#L10-L59\n-->"}